了我的努力"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305301,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"由美，但是……@光靠努力……是没用的啊……"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"才没那回事。@因为……"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305301,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"牧野郁美","narration":"由美知道我至今为止有多努力","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"我能大显身手，是因为@我很幸运有一个好的环境。"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"只要有人能发现郁美的闪光点，"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"那郁美也一定能大放异彩的。"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"就像前辈那样，@绝对还有别人能懂你的可爱之处。"},{"chara":[{"id":800203},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305301}],"textRight":"只要有契机就没问题了！@因为郁美你本来就很可爱嘛！"},{"nameNarration":"牧野郁美","narration":"她总是会认可我","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"哪怕我一直都默默无闻@她也坚信@我是全世界最可爱的那个人"},{"narration":"由美她一直都是如此"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305301}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"嗯……@郁美不会气馁的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305301,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"因为一直闷闷不乐的，@[chara:305301:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:305301:cheek_1][chara:305301:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json][chara:305301:lipSynch_1]才不是郁美的作风嘛！"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"嗯！没问题的！@再过一阵……再过不久就可以啦！"},{"nameNarration":"牧野郁美","narration":"在由美的鼓励之下@我决定再努力一把@那时我觉得没签约是正确的选择","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"因为要是通过许愿当上了偶像@那就等于背叛了由美对我的信任"},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"但现在一想@我当时就应该再好好思考一番才对"},{"narration":"想一想为什么那么烦人的丘比@突然不来找我了"},{"narration":"以及，由美为什么@会那么自信地跟我保证……"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21321.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800400,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305301,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800302,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"id":800400,"mouthOpen":1},